metadata.name: MONEY
metadata.description:
What happens when out of some frustration you throw Midjourney a prompt to create a piece based on the recent FTX drama where you just saw your funds frozen.  
I wanted to create a 70ies style movie poster because that's what this all episode feels like.  
Reserve price is more or less what I lost.  
Royalties are set to 50%, if this ever goes to secondary I'll use the funds to buy art from people in need
